  "description": "A long-distance view of Alcatraz Island and the Golden Gate Bridge under a hazy sky. A small airplane is leaving a long white contrail in the sky above the bridge. Numerous sailboats dot the surrounding bay, creating a busy seascape. The bridge, a distinctive red-orange hue, spans the water with its iconic towers and cables. Alcatraz Island, a dark gray structure, sits prominently in the foreground, and the distant coastline is visible in the background. The overall impression is one of expansive space and iconic San Francisco landmarks.",
